[h2]Compatibility[/h2]
[list][*]The patch is intended to be a part of the [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3580687852]Halloween Ceternity[/url] mod collection.
[*]Compatible with Starbound version 1.4 and above.
[*]Works alongside most mods. If you encounter conflicts, please report them in the Issues section.
[*]Requires all 4 mods listed in the "Affected Mods" section to be installed for full functionality.
[*]Compatible with [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=737353165]Tabula Rasa[/url]: all recipes from the [b]Haunted Crafting Table[/b] (and more) can be accessed through it.[list]
